		introduction: "(Modern Section)<br><br>CCA Sessions: Monday and Thursday (5pm - 8.30pm)<br><br>Venue: SALT Centre Dance Studio at High School Section<br><br>Requirements: Dance background preferred<br><br>How to Join: Auditions<br><br>Participation in Competitions: Yes<br><br>(Street Section)<br><br>CCA Sessions: Tuesday (5-7pm) and Wednesday (3.30pm-5.30pm)<br><br>Venue: SALT Centre Dance Studio at High School Section (Tuesday), Room Under Auditorium (Wednesday)<br><br>Requirements: Dance background preferred<br><br>How to Join: Auditions<br><br>Participation in Competitions: No<br><br>Who to Contact:&nbsp;<br><br>Shuyu, President<br><br>96975927&nbsp;<br><br>Jia Jing, Vice President&nbsp;<br><br>96309973<br><br>",
